About Game:
************
Callie is a travelling smoothie stand owner and her intent is to spread her brand across the globe! Impress your clients by serving them delicious smoothie combinations and appetizers. Travel the globe to develop a blooming business in 10 exciting worlds. Can you win over the approval of food critics, the press and celebrities?
